<script>
import axios from 'axios';
const URL = 'http://localhost:8000/api/name/1';
export default {
  getName() {
    //return axios.get(URL).then(response => response.data);
    return 'aboba';
  },

  updateName(name) {
    return axios.put(URL, name);
  }
}
</script>
